| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0967 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 121fb0cf-455b-5e8c-b7bf-aa2bd5d5691c"
